Thornar drew back on his bowstring with haste and took aim at the base of the ogre’s neck, only moments had pasted but it felt like an eternity. Checking his aim once more Thornar let the bone hooked arrow lose. The arrow in a very disciplined manner struck its target true. The large man stood up straight and began to motion to his neck. <br>
Feign broke free of the tight hold that was set upon him. Without giving it a thought, feign turned and gave a thunderous kick to the chest of the lumbering ogre. <br>
“Feign now, strike now” Thornar bellowed as he ran as hard as he could toward the two. Drawing his sword Thornar was at full tilt, with all the power within him, he hurled himself towards the target. The next moment Thornar was looking up from the flat of his back. He had been knocked off course by a strategic forearm. Gasping for breath Thornar began to speak.<br>
“Marr I ask your blessing upon my sword, help me now I pray to you”<br>
Thornar’s hands began to glow ever so slightly, and he sprang to his feet. Closing in Thornar with an open hand made a motion toward the ogre, and a red aura cleansed the pungent being. <br>
Seeing the ogre stunned, feign began his second attack. Kicking and punching. Thornar immediately began to taunt the ogre as he swung his gold handled sword. The ogre turned to Thornar’s attacks. <br>
The ogre was trying to heal himself mid battle, but Thornar would not let up from stunning his opponent, over and over.<br>
“Karana, make your voice the sound of a thousand seas” Thornar shouted.<br>
The ogre’s head filled with a defining roar. The thunder of Karana was let lose upon him. The ogre could feel the mana seeping from his body. The ogre turned and began to run.<br>
“Eye of newt, frogy meat, a large ogre can’t move his feet” The ogre stopped and stood still for a brief second then fell to the ground with a thud.  <br>
